    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('Get emails to send reminders').item.json.Email }}",
        "subject": "={{ $('Get emails to send reminders').item.json['Startup Name'] }} has been approved to pitch with {{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[2].VALUE }}",
        "message": "=\n\nDear {{ $('Get emails to send reminders').item.json.Name }},<br><br>\n\nWe are excited to invite you to present your startup at the upcoming {{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[2].VALUE }} Investment Committee, scheduled to take place on:<br><br>\n\n<b>Day:</b> {{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[3].VALUE }}<br>\n<b>Time:</b> {{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[4].VALUE }}. Your pitch starting at {{ $('Route right message').item.json['Time of pitching'] }}<br>\n<b>Location:</b> {{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[5].VALUE }}<br><br>\n\n<b>What to Expect:</b><br><br>\n\nYou’ll be one of the few startups pitching to our angel investors during this session. The format is as follows:<br><br>\n\n- 15 minutes for your pitch presentation<br>\n- 30 minutes for Q&A with our investors<br><br>\n\nPlease ensure your presentation is sharp, focused, and <b>includes the core investment information.</b><br><br>\n\n<b>Logistics & Deadlines:</b><br><br>\n\n- Slide Deck: Please send your final presentation by <b>{{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[6].VALUE }}</b>, so we can prepare everything on our side.<br>\n- Pre-Pitch information: <b>Please fill out this document as soon as possible</b>, so the investors have all important information about you gathered: <a href=\"{{ $('Route right message').item.json['Pre Pitch Document link'] }}\">this document here</a>.<br>\n- Participation online: Please join the session 5 min prior to your pitch.<br>\n- Participation in person: Please arrive at the location 15 min prior to your pitch.<br><br>\n\n<b>After the IC:</b><br><br>\n\nInvestors will have two weeks to cast their votes. In the first week, they may submit additional questions in a shared document which we’ll forward to you. You can respond at your own pace.<br><br>\n\nWe’re looking forward to your pitch and to facilitating meaningful conversations with our investors.<br><br>\n\nIf you have any questions or need support preparing, don’t hesitate to reach out.<br><br>\n\nHave a great day,<br>\n<i>Sarah</i>\n",
        "options": {
          "appendAttribution": false
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        1552,
        -16
      ],
      "id": "f7070b54-d2a5-49f5-b446-7b1915702838",
