        "subject": "={{ $('Get emails to send reminders').item.json['Startup Name'] }}'s next step after the Investment Committee.",
        "message": "=Hello {{ $('Get emails to send reminders').item.json.Name }},<br><br>\n\nThank you for your pitch yesterday. <b>The investors are now discussing the startups.</b><br><br>\n\nIn order to give them the opportunity to ask further questions, we created <b><a href=\"{{ $('Route right message').item.json['Document link']}}\">this document.</a></b><br><br>\n\nIf they have any questions, they will add them there.<br><br> \n\nThey have the deadline to ask further questions until next <b>{{ $('Aggregate variables values').item.json.data[7].VALUE }}</b>. Please make sure to also answer their questions by then.<br><br>\n\nThank you and have a great day,<br>\n<i>Sarah</i>",
